CNCP v1 24898
{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#12110: Using unions in defineProps in conjunction with withDefaults breaks emits type inference",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:22:07.831045+00:00",
  "text": "Using unions in defineProps in conjunction with withDefaults breaks emits type inference\n\n### Vue version\n\n3.5.11\n\n### Link to minimal reproduction\n\nhttps://play.vuejs.org/#\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nThe SFC Playground is a bit broken because even if you remove `withDefaults` it still won't be able to infer the type if you hover on the emit with your mouse. So I suggest to copy paste the code locally: vscode will be able to infer the event type once you remove `withDefaults`.\r\n\r\nAlternatively you can try to assign the event to a function which expects a different type and run `vue-tsc --build --force`.\r\nWithout `withDefaults` it will complain about the mismatch:\r\n![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3ad3079a-37ad-4df8-a5a8-709a9aede253)\r\n\r\nIf you leave `withDefaults` it won't complain because he thinks the inferred type is any:\r\n![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/148b3223-27ff-4bbc-971e-0c3a199a8c1e)\n\n### What is expected?\n\nUsing `withDefaults` in conjuction with union props shouldn't break emits type inference.\n\n### What is actually happening?\n\nUsing `withDefaults` in conjuction with union props breaks emits type inference.\r\n\r\nThis is without `withDefaults`:\r\n![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/77e75bef-f271-42b7-84ca-2821150329a5)\r\n\r\nWhile this is with `withDefaults`:\r\n![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/775955c9-f98f-4825-8fdc-2866c4d745bf)\n\n### System Info\n\n```shell\nSystem:\r\n    OS: Linux 6.10 Arch Linux\r\n    CPU: (16) x64 AMD Ryzen 9 PRO 7940HS w/ Radeon 780M Graphics\r\n    Memory: 26.39 GB / 58.64 GB\r\n    Container: Yes\r\n    Shell: 5.2.37 - /bin/bash\r\n  Binaries:\r\n    Node: 20.17.0 - /run/user/1000/fnm_multishells/57865_1728023771872/bin/node\r\n    Yarn: 4.5.0 - /run/user/1000/fnm_multishells/57865_1728023771872/bin/yarn\r\n    npm: 10.8.2 - /run/user/1000/fnm_multishells/57865_1728023771872/bin/npm\r\n    Watchman: 20240414.112832.0 - /usr/bin/watchman\r\n  Browsers:\r\n    Chromium: 129.0.6668.89\r\n  npmPackages:\r\n    vue: ^3.5.11 => 3.5.11\n```\n\n\n### Any additional comments?\n\n_No response_",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    "scope: types",
    "language-tools"
  ],
